      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BORACAY STORM (5) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 25.24 beating Weblec Whistler. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from six starts. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. COMICAL WARREN (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (25.71) in a Mix 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Expected to feature in the finish. VERACIOUS VAL (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this journey with four wins and a placing from nine tries. Recorded a nose win (30.27) in a Mix 5 last time at Q Parklands. Among the main chances. CLEAN ENGINES (7) proved himself from this box last start so warrants respect.",
